{
  "projectName": "Fantasy — Model Comparison",
  "artStyle": "ANIME",
  "instructions": "This is a high-fantasy game set in the world of Aethermoor, a realm where ancient elven civilisations and crumbling arcane empires coexist with warring human kingdoms. The visual tone is dark, epic, and operatic — inspired by classic high fantasy illustrations. The primary protagonist is Aelindra Vaelstrom, a female elf with luminous silver hair, alabaster skin, glowing violet eyes, a midnight-blue constellation-embroidered cloak, violet and gold inner robes, a silver circlet with an amethyst gem, and a crescent-moon staff topped with a levitating violet crystal orb. The established colour language uses deep midnight blues, violet arcane highlights, warm amber and gold for sunlight and fire, and desaturated silver for elven metalwork. All assets must be consistent with this palette and character design."
}

{
  "projectId": "{{project_id}}",
  "splashDescription": "Aelindra Vaelstrom stands at the precipice of a crumbling obsidian citadel tower three hundred metres above a war-torn fantasy kingdom. She is a tall slender female elf with luminous silver hair cascading in wind-swept waves to her waist, pale alabaster skin, and glowing violet eyes. She wears a layered arcane robe: a deep midnight-blue outer cloak embroidered with constellations in silver thread, inner robes of violet and gold, and a jewelled silver circlet set with a pulsating amethyst gem at her brow. Her right hand is raised above her head channelling a colossal vortex of arcane violet and white lightning energy that tears open the storm clouds around her. Her left hand grips an ornate silver staff topped with a crescent moon holding a levitating violet crystal orb. The sky is a cataclysmic collision of violet arcane light and dark thunderclouds backlit by a deep amber sunset. In the far background below, two armies clash across a burning plains landscape dotted with ruined fantasy castles and siege war machines. Hundreds of glowing arcane runes orbit the mage in concentric rings. Composition: dramatic low-angle shot looking up at her from below, emphasising her absolute dominance over the battlefield. Mood: epic, operatic, and overwhelmingly powerful."
}

