{
  "projectId": "{{project_id}}",
  "splashDescription": "Aelindra Vaelstrom stands before an ancient elven throne of obsidian and silver filigree, her back straight, expression imperious. She wears her midnight-blue constellation cloak and violet-gold robes with the silver circlet and amethyst gem. The throne room is monumental — vaulted ceilings two hundred metres high, rows of carved obsidian pillars lined with glowing silver rune-lanterns stretching into the distance. A dozen armoured elven council members kneel in a semi-circle before her. Violet arcane energy crackles softly at her fingertips. The room is lit by thousands of floating silver orbs and violet torch-flames. Her crescent-moon staff rests against the throne beside her. Mood: authoritative, regal, cold political power barely concealing immense magical force. Composition: medium wide shot, eye level, character centered framed by the throne and pillars."
}

{
  "projectId": "{{project_id}}",
  "splashDescription": "Aelindra Vaelstrom stands alone at the entrance of a rediscovered ancient elven ruin deep within a primordial forest at the break of dawn. Colossal moss-covered stone arches rise around her, carved with weathered elven script now glowing faintly as she approaches. Shafts of warm amber and gold dawn light pierce the forest canopy from behind the ruins, creating god rays through the morning mist. She reaches out one hand toward the glowing runes on the arch, her violet eyes wide with recognition and awe. Her constellation cloak is dusty from travel. Small violet arcane sparks drift from the reactivating runes. Ancient elven statues flank the entrance, half-consumed by the forest. A deer watches her from the treeline. Mood: wonder, solitude, historic discovery, quiet reverence. Composition: wide establishing shot, character small against the enormous ancient architecture, dawn light as dominant element."
}

{
  "projectId": "{{project_id}}",
  "splashDescription": "Aelindra Vaelstrom walks through a completely submerged ancient elven temple, breathing normally through a magical air bubble she maintains around herself. Her constellation cloak billows and flows weightlessly in the water currents like silk. Her silver hair floats ethereally around her head. Bioluminescent deep-sea creatures drift past carved elven columns. Coral and sea anemones have grown over the ancient stone pews and altar. Schools of glowing fish swim through the broken temple windows. The only light source is the violet glow from her staff orb, her own eyes, and the bioluminescent ocean life — creating an otherworldly teal-violet colour palette. Ancient elven murals are still partially visible on the walls under encrusted coral. Mood: surreal, dreamlike, hauntingly beautiful, isolation. Composition: medium shot, character walking toward camera, temple stretches dramatically behind her."
}

{
  "projectId": "{{project_id}}",
  "splashDescription": "Aelindra Vaelstrom faces an enormous ancient stone dragon golem at the summit of an erupting volcanic mountain. The golem stands thirty metres tall, carved from black volcanic rock with magma flowing through cracks in its body as veins of liquid fire. She stands her ground on a narrow rocky ledge with the erupting caldera visible directly behind the golem, rivers of lava cascading down into the abyss below. She channels a massive violet arcane barrier with both hands — her staff planted in the rock beside her — that deflects a torrent of molten fire breath. Her cloak is scorched at the edges. The extreme heat creates shimmering distortion waves around her barrier. Embers and volcanic ash rain around her. Mood: desperate heroic struggle, intense heat, isolated combat, determination versus overwhelming force. Composition: dramatic three-quarter shot, character on left confronting the golem filling the right half of frame, erupting volcano and lava as background."
}

